  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baf \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The police's request to the court to stop tomorrow's demonstration was rejected",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A massive public protest against the government will be held on Saturday 9th tomorrow.",
        "It is known that 8 thousand additional police and army personnel have been called for the security of Colombo while a massive demonstration is going to be held to demand the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa on the 9th of Saturday.",
        "In this case, the judge rejected the request made by the Kollupitiya Police in front of the Colombo Additional Judge Bandara Ilangasinghe to issue an order to stop the demonstration that will be held tomorrow on the 9th.",
        "At the same time, Malikavatth police have asked Colombo Additional Magistrate R.N.L. The judge also rejected the request made in front of Mahawat.",
        "Yesterday on the 07th, religious clerics started protesting against the current rulers demanding the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapasha and the government.",
        "In this case, Colombo Chief Justice Nandana Amarasinghe rejected the request made by the Karuwathota Police to the Colombo Chief Justice's Court to issue an order to stop the demonstration of the All University Students' Union.",
        "Meanwhile, it is worth noting that there will be a massive public protest against the government on Saturday, the 9th of tomorrow."
      ],
